#
#### install rust for lua formatting
```bash
curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs | sh
cargo --version
cargo install stylua
```

### install
```bash
	brew install neovim
```

### nerd fonts (dev icons)
```bash
  brew tap homebrew/cask-fonts
  brew install font-mononoki-nerd-font
```

